            <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;text-decoration: underline;&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;size-medium wp-image-496 alignnone&#34; title=&#34;ifleea&#34; src=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/name-300x187.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;ifleea&#34; width=&#34;400&#34; height=&#34;250&#34; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;这周专业课的作业多到让人恶心。上图是自己设计所谓“名片”。曾老师说“这怎么说明你是设计师呢？”我不想泄漏自己这个小角落，就没有说这是我博客的地址。毕竟言论自由不想要自己的长辈干预。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;另外一个设计作业，设计“361度”的鞋子。我们前期已经做了充分的调研工作。这次要做的是三张手绘和一张PS稿。下面发图上来吧，打字累。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel=&#34;attachment wp-att-503&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/495.html/linane589afe69cac&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-medium wp-image-503&#34; title=&#34;PS稿&#34; src=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/linane589afe69cac-300x237.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;PS稿&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;237&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel=&#34;attachment wp-att-502&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/495.html/attachment/11&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-medium wp-image-502&#34; title=&#34;设计手绘1&#34; src=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/11-300x212.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;设计手绘1&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;212&#34; srcset=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/11-300x212.jpg 300w, https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/11.jpg 545w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel=&#34;attachment wp-att-501&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/495.html/attachment/3&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-medium wp-image-501&#34; title=&#34;设计手绘3&#34; src=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/3-300x209.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;设计手绘3&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;209&#34; srcset=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/3-300x209.jpg 300w, https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/3.jpg 555w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel=&#34;attachment wp-att-500&#34; href=&#34;https://blog.natt.cc/495.html/attachment/2&#34;&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; decoding=&#34;async&#34; class=&#34;alignnone size-medium wp-image-500&#34; title=&#34;设计手绘3&#34; src=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/2-300x208.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;设计手绘3&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;208&#34; srcset=&#34;https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/2-300x208.jpg 300w, https://blognew.natt.cc/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/2.jpg 555w&#34; sizes=&#34;auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;就这样吧。就算我是个设计师吧。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;周末还要平面作业要做。到时候再写写吧。&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</description>
